**Summary:** This documentation explains how to create and configure recommendation sets for the Resource Center, which are customizable in-time articles and information that can be embedded throughout websites as personalized landing pages with various action types including visit link, click element, run callback, open third party chat, show guide/survey, open article, and play video.

